{title: Happy Birthday To Me}
{artist: Hank Locklin}
{composer: Written by Bill Anderson}

[G]Today has been my birthday and [C]tonight I should be [G]glad
But [C]you weren't here to share [G]it and [A7]inside I've hurt so [D7]bad
